name: Elvy Sukaesih
description: '''Elvy Sukaesih''' (born 25 June 1951) is an Indonesian  [[dangdut]] singer and actress who has been dubbed the Queen of Dangdut. Sukaesih has a significant fan base in other Asian countries such as [[Japan]].  She has been a prolific recording artist since the late 1960s. {{Citation needed|date=January 2009}}
